EmailTemplate.subject: Nokia/TM Forum webinar April 26: Monetization in a 5G world
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Thank you for your interest in our webinar – Additional resources available View as web page <[[{{system.viewAsWebpageLink}}]]> Thank you for your interest in our April 26 webinar: Monetization in a 5G world As a reminder, you can access a brochure summarizing the session here <[[https://resources.nokia.com/asset/205109?did=d000000000eu&utm_campaign=service_innovation&utm_source=email-list-tmfwebinar-attendees&utm_medium=email&utm_content=brochure]]>.
You can also download the two white papers that were mentioned during the session:
- Deploying cloud-native revenue management applications <[[https://resources.nokia.com/asset/201360?did=d000000000ev&utm_campaign=service_innovation&utm_source=email-list-tmfwebinar-attendees&utm_medium=email&utm_content=wp-cloud-native-revenue-mgmt]]> - Enabling Digital Partners <[[https://resources.nokia.com/asset/201381?did=d000000000ew&utm_campaign=service_innovation&utm_source=email-list-tmfwebinar-attendees&utm_medium=email&utm_content=enabling-digital-partners]]>
Please do not hesitate to contact us for further information. Also, you can visit our website <[[https://networks.nokia.com/solutions/monetization]]> to learn more.
Best regards, Steffen Paulus Head of Revenue Management Marketing, Nokia Connect with us © {{my.CopyrightYear}} Nokia.
